"New Game" View
- Ability to accept a punishment and it change the result in persistent memory
    - The ablity to decline and do nothing

"All Punishments" View
- Add new punishment inside of the Punishments view
    - Pick from "Low, Medium, High" likelihood from a slide picker
        - High = get highest existing number in punishmentsMap
        - Low = get lowest existing number in the punishmentsMap
        - Med = Average of the two
- Drop down that allows filtering by highest percentage likelihood
- Search for a punishment

"Game Stats"
- List view of Tables
    - Each table has Game: 1/2/3/4..., First: name, Second: name, etc. then Punishment: description, Completed: Yes/No
